    <h1>Negative SEO</h1>
    <p class="description">Malicious tactics aimed at <strong>sabotaging a competitor's search rankings</strong> — through toxic link building, content scraping, hacking, or fake reviews. 65% of SEO professionals have encountered attacks on their clients.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
